main_body:
The TFEU shall consequently be amended as follows:
1. in the first paragraph of Article 349, the words ‘Saint-Barthélemy’ shall be deleted;
2. in Article 355(1), the words ‘Saint-Barthélemy’ shall be deleted;
3. in Annex II, an indent shall be inserted, between that relating to ‘Saint Pierre and Miquelon’ and that relating to ‘Aruba’, which shall read as follows:
‘— Saint-Barthélemy,’.
